<QuestionText><![CDATA[You want to load an image of a toy in a <font face="courier new">PictureBox</font> control. Which one of the following codes will help you to achieve this?]]></QuestionText>
<Options>
	<Option><![CDATA[<font face="courier new">PictureBox picBook = new PictureBox();<br>picBook.Name = "picToyImage";<br>picBook.Text = "TeddyBear";<br>picBook.SetImage = "image01.jpg";<br>picBook.SetBounds(10, 10, 150, 200);<br>picBook.SizeMode = PictureBoxSizeMode.StretchImage;</font><br>]]></Option>
	<Option><![CDATA[<font face="courier new">PictureBox picBook = new PictureBox();<br>picBook.Name = "picToyImage";<br>picBook.Text = "TeddyBear";<br>picBook.ImageLocation = "image01.jpg";<br>picBook.SetBounds(10, 10, 150, 200);<br>picBook.SizeMode = PictureBoxSizeMode.StretchImage;</font><br>]]></Option>
	<Option><![CDATA[<font face="courier new">PictureBox picBook = new PictureBox();<br>picBook.Name = "picToyImage";<br>picBook.Text = "TeddyBear";<br>picBook.SetImageLocation = "image01.jpg";<br>picBook.SetBounds(10, 10, 150, 200);<br>picBook.SizeMode = PictureBoxSizeMode.StretchImage;</font><br>]]></Option>
	<Option><![CDATA[<font face="courier new">PictureBox picBook = new PictureBox();<br>picBook.Name = "picToyImage";<br>picBook.Text = "TeddyBear";<br>picBook.GetImageLocation = "image01.jpg";<br>picBook.SetBounds(10, 10, 150, 200);<br>picBook.SizeMode = PictureBoxSizeMode.StretchImage;</font><br>]]></Option>
</Options>
